data.description: NO HOA!! This charming 3/4 brick house sits on a sprawling .51-acre lot, perfectly situated near Kyle and a convenient commuting distance to downtown Austin. With a brand-new roof and updated siding on the rear, this home boasts both durability and style. Step onto the extended covered patio, a prime spot for enjoying outdoor living and entertaining. Solar window screens add energy efficiency to the mix, keeping your indoor spaces comfortable year-round. Inside, you'll find a fully finished garage making it a versatile space for hobbies, workouts, or parking. The garage's finished flooring adds a polished touch. No need to worry about hard water – a water softener system is already in place. Stay comfortable in every season with the newer HVAC system. The house is a blank canvas awaiting your decorative touch, allowing you to make it truly your own. Don't miss the opportunity to own this gem, offering a mix of modern upgrades and potential for personalization. Experience the tranquility of suburban living while staying connected to city amenities. Your Texas dream home is ready and waiting!
